  "prompt": "What is the best apps for learning how to sing english songs with audio check?",
  "response": "There are several apps that can help you learn to sing English songs while providing audio feedback. Here are some of the best options available:\n\n1. **Smule**: This karaoke app allows you to sing along with a huge library of songs. It provides audio effects, and you can get feedback on your singing. You can also collaborate with other singers.\n\n2. **Yousician**: Primarily known for learning musical instruments, Yousician also offers vocal lessons. It provides real-time feedback on your singing and helps you improve through guided exercises and songs.\n\n3. **Singscope**: This app offers a visual representation of your singing. You can record your voice and see how well you match the pitch of the original song. It's a great tool for self-assessment.\n\n4. **Vocal Coach**: This app is designed to help you improve your singing technique, with exercises and feedback. It focuses on vocal training and provides audio examples to sing along with.\n\n5. **Sing Sharp**: This app offers vocal training exercises and allows you to practice singing songs. It includes pitch detection and provides feedback, helping you refine your skills.\n\n6. **Riff Studio**: This app allows you to record your voice while singing along with songs. You can adjust the pitch and tempo of the music, making it easier to practice.\n\n7. **Warm Me Up**: A vocal warm-up app that helps you prepare your voice before singing. It includes exercises and scales to improve your vocal range and flexibility.\n\n8. **Karaoke Apps (like Karafun or Karaoke by Tuner)**: Although primarily for karaoke, these apps often have pitch detection features that can help you understand how accurately you're hitting notes while singing along with songs from their libraries.\n\nWhen choosing an app, consider what features are most important to you, such as song selection, feedback mechanisms, or vocal training exercises. Many of these apps offer free trials, so you can test them out to see which works best for you.",
